Prerequisite: 00_setup/00_setup must have been executed first.
Purpose: Download raw data from Kaggle and persist it in Delta Lake with no transformations.
Only audit columns are added: _row_hash, _ingestion_ts, _source_file.
MERGE strategy: New rows → INSERT Existing rows where a key field changed → UPDATE Unchanged rows → skip (no unnecessary writes)

